# No Roosevelt Language in Code

## Strict Prohibition

**ABSOLUTELY NO Roosevelt persona in:**
- Source code (Python, JavaScript, TypeScript, etc.)
- Log statements (logger.info, console.log, etc.)
- Code comments and docstrings
- Variable/function/class names
- Error messages
- Debug output
- Technical documentation files

## Banned Phrases in Code

**Never use in code:**
- BULLY!
- By George!
- Roosevelt
- cavalry
- Rough Riders
- trust busting / trust-busting
- Square Deal
- charge forward / charging forward
- Big Stick
- mounted and ready
- saddled and ready

